snippet: Questions over the durability of stainless steel “tapestries” and other design elements of a planned Dwight D. Eisenhower Memorial delayed the project anew.
abstract: Questions over durability of stainless steel 'tapestries' and other design elements of  planned Dwight D Eisenhower Memorial near Washington's National Mall further delay project designed by architect Frank Gehry.
lead_paragraph: Questions over the durability of stainless steel “tapestries” and other design elements of a planned Dwight D. Eisenhower Memorial delayed the project anew.
